00:42:47.300 --> 00:42:50.300
Given that why do you
think people are just

00:42:50.300 --> 00:42:57.970
so obsessed and interested
in kids like Tom-- sorry,

00:42:57.970 --> 00:42:59.180
kids like Taylor?

00:42:59.180 --> 00:43:01.346
TOM CLYNES: I wish they
were obsessed and interested

00:43:01.346 --> 00:43:03.050
