So they were able to bring in
mentors, and other learning

00:49:21.950 --> 00:49:26.200
opportunities, and really
take him places far away.

00:49:26.200 --> 00:49:28.320
And I think that
was something that

00:49:28.320 --> 00:49:30.760
was just sort of instinctive.

00:49:30.760 --> 00:49:33.160
I talked to one person,
a child psychologist

00:49:33.160 --> 00:49:34.780
David Feldman, that
studied these sort

00:49:34.780 --> 00:49:36.990
of super precocious kids.

00:49:36.990 --> 00:49:40.950
And he had an interesting theory
