00:49:43.800 --> 00:49:46.590
But it's because he can't
explain it any other way.

00:49:46.590 --> 00:49:52.680
Well maybe just as there might
have been a scientist somewhere

00:49:52.680 --> 00:49:57.590
back in the gene pool
